# Platform Architecture Portfolio

**Enterprise Platform Architecture | Kubernetes | GitOps | DevSecOps | Observability | AI Infrastructure Readiness**

This repository is an architecture-first portfolio with a small production-style demo layer.

It shows how an enterprise platform can be structured around:

- Internal Developer Platforms
- Kubernetes platform engineering
- GitOps operating models
- Secure-by-default workload delivery
- Observability and reliability
- Platform service contracts
- Compliance-aware governance patterns
- AI infrastructure readiness

The deployable demo is intentionally small, but the surrounding architecture, repo structure, contracts, controls, and deployment patterns reflect how real platform teams package reusable capabilities.

> This repository is fully generalized. It does not include confidential company names, customer data, internal network information, production IPs, or proprietary implementation details.

